00:10:13.040 --> 00:10:14.840
that Rockwell is encountering.

00:10:14.840 --> 00:10:18.840
So on your table, you'll each
have a small size of these

00:10:18.840 --> 00:10:19.910
so you can refer to it.

00:10:19.910 --> 00:10:22.250
And then each of the
groups has a larger version

00:10:22.250 --> 00:10:24.740
up on the easel charts.

00:10:24.740 --> 00:10:27.860
So each of the tables is going
to be working with a group.

00:10:27.860 --> 00:10:30.230
And you're going to
