00:10:30.230 --> 00:10:33.650
responds to question 8
in the case study, which

00:10:33.650 --> 00:10:36.350
is, "Suppose you are
the RPI team leader

00:10:36.350 --> 00:10:38.930
and have to report
back to Joanie.

00:10:38.930 --> 00:10:41.380
What will you recommend?"

00:10:41.380 --> 00:10:43.960
So we'd like you to spend
about 20 minutes preparing

00:10:43.960 --> 00:10:46.690
with your team at
the table an A3 plan.

00:10:46.690 --> 00:10:47.200
All right.

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:48.908
And we've given you
the template that you

00:10:48.908 --> 00:10:50.300
