00:11:02.770 --> 00:11:05.890
So make sure you think
about all stakeholders.

00:11:05.890 --> 00:11:08.350
Then you'll want to verify
that the information we've

00:11:08.350 --> 00:11:11.440
provided to you on
those sheets is correct.

00:11:11.440 --> 00:11:13.060
Complete the
additional information

00:11:13.060 --> 00:11:15.640
blocks that are in the template.

00:11:15.640 --> 00:11:18.490
And you can use some of the
